- Costs incurred to secure customer orders and deliver goods/services are generally represented by "Selling Expenses".
- Financing costs incurred to raise funds are generally represented by "Financial Expenses".
- Systematic allocation of depreciable amount is represented by "Depreciation".
- Total amount of taxes expected to be paid or recovered is "Tax Expense".
